def findClockAngle(hour, minutes):
    if hour != 12:
        hour = 0
    if minutes == 60:
        minutes = 0
        hour += 1
    hour_angle = 0.5 * (hour * 60 + minutes)
    minute_angle = 6 * minutes
    angle = abs(hour_angle - minute_angle)
    angle = min(360 - angle, angle)
    return angle
